  ('pukao-8ec6300d-moex-00016', 'pukao-8ec6300d', 'pukao-8ec6300d-moex-114-156cbda0', 'sub-pukao-8ec6300d-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '對於圖的定義，所謂簡圖（SimpleGraph），下列敘述何者正確？', '["以相鄰矩陣（AdjacencyMatrices）表示該圖，其主對角線上的值均為0", "對於簡單有向圖（SimpleDirectedGraph），則兩節點（u,v）之間僅允許一個邊，亦即（u→v）或是（v→u） 的任一個", "對於簡單有向圖，相鄰矩陣上的數字會有0,1,或2的數值", "該圖允許某些節點可以直接連接自我的節點，稱為自我迴圈（SelfLoops）"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:35:41+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "ebba180acb37", "answer_pdf_sha1": "b58c95b8bfaa", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114080", "c": "447", "s": "2504", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "計算機概要", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年公務人員高等考試三級考試暨普通考試", "original_question_number": 16, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "pukao", "civil_category": "電信工程"}'::jsonb, NULL),
